{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/playlog-december-2018-grim-fandango-remastered","webpackCompilationHash":"c5fd97f60566efd6d603","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"repo":"kvadevack/site","social":{"twitter":"kvadevack","github":"kvadevack"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Grim Fandango remains one of my all-time favorite video games, and the remaster stays true to the original. The setting,\nmusic, and writing are superb. It oozes charm, creativity, and a sense of atmosphere that sets it apart from many other\nadventure games. But the faithful recreation leaves several gameplay aspects showing their age.<!-- jump --></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/1f853/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gfs 419299 2 5\"\n        title=\"The humor is on point.\"\n        src=\"/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/a111b/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/aca85/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg 163w,\n/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/0954f/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg 325w,\n/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/a111b/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg 650w,\n/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/ce471/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg 975w,\n/static/374a1517e804444c971034de812a4d18/1f853/gfs_419299_2_5.jpg 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">The humor is on point.</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Inventory management is slow, some lengthy transitions between screens are unskippable, and some of the most obtuse\npuzzles created by LucasArts in the 90's are still in this game. But despite its flaws, it's still an amazing experience!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Playlog December 2018: Grim Fandango Remastered","date":"December 21st 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"playlog-december-2018-grim-fandango-remastered","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"cxx-modules"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"nintendo-switch-virtual-keyboard"}},"hasExample":false}}}